<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٩٢٤ - أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2711">‌سُوَيْدُ بْنُ نَصْرٍ </a>قَالَ: أَنْبَأَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3875">‌عَبْدُ اللهِ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6932">‌يَحْيَى بْنِ سَعِيدٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4781">‌عَمْرَةَ </a>أَنَّهَا سَمِعَتْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">‌عَائِشَةَ </a>تَقُولُ <span class="c2">«يُقْطَعُ فِي رُبُعِ دِينَارٍ فَصَاعِدًا»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>قَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/9712">‌أَبُو عَبْدِ الرَّحْمَنِ </a>: هَذَا الصَّوَابُ مِنْ حَدِيثِ يَحْيَى.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>